---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Verdex Soluciones Circulares | Transformando el futuro de los residuos"
  description="Verdex ofrece soluciones integrales de economía circular, gestionando de forma sostenible y eficiente los recursos para proteger el medio ambiente."
>
  <header class="fixed w-full z-50 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-slate-200/50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex justify-start items-center h-20">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <!-- Logo Placeholder -->
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-teal-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl shadow-lg shadow-emerald-500/20">
            V
          </div>
          <span class="font-bold text-xl tracking-tight text-slate-800">Verdex</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-48 lg:pb-32 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top_right,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-emerald-100/40 via-slate-50 to-slate-50"></div>
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-8 items-center">
          <div class="max-w-2xl">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-100/50 text-emerald-800 text-sm font-medium mb-6 border border-emerald-200/50">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse"></span>
              Economía Circular
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-6 leading-[1.1]">
              El ciclo de la <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-600 to-teal-500">sostenibilidad</span>.
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
              Transformamos residuos en recursos. En Verdex implementamos soluciones de economía circular que reducen el impacto ambiental y optimizan los procesos de tu empresa.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
              <a href="#contacto" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3.5 text-base font-medium text-white bg-slate-900 rounded-full hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-0.5">
                Solicitar Diagnóstico
              </a>
              <a href="#servicios" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3.5 text-base font-medium text-slate-700 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-full hover:bg-slate-50 hover:border-slate-300 transition-all shadow-sm">
                Conocer Más
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative lg:ml-auto w-full max-w-lg aspect-square lg:aspect-[4/5] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl ring-1 ring-slate-900/10">
            <img src="/images/hero.png" alt="Verdex - Innovación en Economía Circular" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-900/40 to-transparent"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Logo Cloud / Trust -->
    <section class="py-12 bg-white border-y border-slate-100">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <p class="text-center text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-8">Empresas que confían en nuestro modelo circular</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-8 md:gap-16 opacity-50 grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500">
          <div class="h-8 flex items-center font-bold text-xl text-slate-400">EcoTech</div>
          <div class="h-8 flex items-center font-bold text-xl text-slate-400">NaturaWorks</div>
          <div class="h-8 flex items-center font-bold text-xl text-slate-400">GreenLogistics</div>
          <div class="h-8 flex items-center font-bold text-xl text-slate-400">SustainCorp</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services Section -->
    <section id="servicios" class="py-24 relative">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-4">Nuestras Soluciones</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">Implementamos estrategias integrales que cierran el ciclo de vida de los materiales, generando valor ambiental y económico.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Service Card 1 -->
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-emerald-100 transition-all group">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-emerald-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-emerald-100 transition-all">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-7 h-7 text-emerald-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Gestión de Residuos</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Clasificación, recolección y tratamiento avanzado de residuos industriales para su reincorporación a la cadena productiva.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Service Card 2 -->
          <div class="bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-lg border border-slate-800 hover:shadow-2xl hover:border-slate-700 transition-all relative overflow-hidden group">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500/10 to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-white/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 backdrop-blur-sm group-hover:scale-110 transition-all relative z-10">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-7 h-7 text-emerald-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 relative z-10">Consultoría Circular</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed relative z-10">Diseñamos estrategias a medida para optimizar el uso de recursos y certificar los procesos bajo estándares internacionales.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Service Card 3 -->
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-emerald-100 transition-all group">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-emerald-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-emerald-100 transition-all">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-7 h-7 text-emerald-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Valorización Energética</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Transformamos materiales no reciclables en fuentes alternativas de energía, reduciendo la dependencia de combustibles fósiles.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Split Section with Image -->
    <section id="impacto" class="py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
          <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden aspect-[4/3] shadow-lg">
            <img src="/images/process.png" alt="Procesos Sostenibles Verdex" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
          </div>
          <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
            <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-6">Medimos lo que importa.</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
              La transición hacia un modelo circular no solo beneficia al planeta, sino que optimiza la rentabilidad operativa. Acompañamos a nuestros clientes con métricas claras y trazabilidad total.
            </p>
            
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-10">
              <div>
                <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-emerald-600 mb-2">95%</div>
                <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-800 mb-1">Recuperación de Materiales</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-slate-500">Promedio en nuestros proyectos industriales.</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-emerald-600 mb-2">-40%</div>
                <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-800 mb-1">Huella de Carbono</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-slate-500">Reducción estimada en los primeros 2 años.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Trazabilidad digital de cada tonelada gestionada.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Reportes ESG listos para auditorías internacionales.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section id="contacto" class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-900"></div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_center,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-emerald-900/40 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Inicia tu transición circular hoy.</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Déjanos tus datos y un especialista de Verdex se pondrá en contacto para evaluar el potencial de circularidad en tu empresa.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Formulario Provisorio -->
        <form class="bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 shadow-2xl max-w-md mx-auto">
          <div class="space-y-4 text-left">
            <div>
              <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 mb-1">Nombre Completo</label>
              <input type="text" id="name" class="w-full bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-white placeholder-slate-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 transition-all" placeholder="Ej. Ana Martínez" required>
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="empresa" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 mb-1">Empresa</label>
              <input type="text" id="empresa" class="w-full bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-white placeholder-slate-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 transition-all" placeholder="Nombre de tu empresa" required>
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 mb-1">Correo Electrónico</label>
              <input type="email" id="email" class="w-full bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-white placeholder-slate-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 transition-all" placeholder="hola@empresa.com" required>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-emerald-500 hover:bg-emerald-400 text-slate-900 font-bold px-6 py-3.5 rounded-xl transition-all shadow-lg shadow-emerald-500/25 mt-4">
              Enviar Solicitud
            </button>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-4 text-center">
            Sitio web en construcción. Estaremos en línea con nuestra plataforma completa muy pronto.
          </p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="bg-slate-950 py-12 border-t border-slate-900">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-teal-600 rounded flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold shadow-lg shadow-emerald-500/20">
          V
        </div>
        <span class="font-bold text-lg text-white">Verdex</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">
        &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Verdex Soluciones Circulares. Todos los derechos reservados.
      </p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
